    "description": "Space Engineers Space Engineers：Warfare 2 “Broadside”包包括Warfare离子推进器、Warfare反应堆、Warfare吊门变体、Warfare火箭发射器、Warfare加特林机枪、探照灯、桥窗、乘客长椅、灯光面板、舵、Warfare电池、散热口、滑动舱门、林地迷彩装甲皮肤、鲨鱼嘴头盔皮肤、“石头剪刀布”表情、“敬礼”表情<br><br>此内容不是“付费即赢”内容，包的拥有者对其他玩家没有优势。 如果你决定不购买“Warfare 2: Broadside”包，但想与购买了“Warfare 2: Broadside”的朋友或其他玩家一同游玩，你仍然能够与他们一起加入多人游戏或服务器并参与游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warfare离子推进器</h2>令人耳目一新的离子推进器。 这些新的推进器是模块化的，可以实现更复杂、更有想象力的布置。 这些推进器可用于小型和大型网格飞船，并且提供多种设计。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/c5270d91d4868b6bdc2d37d2416e0651.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/c5270d91d4868b6bdc2d37d2416e0651.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/c5270d91d4868b6bdc2d37d2416e0651.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warfare反应堆</h2>新版本的标志性核反应堆。 可用于大型和小型网格。 在接近反应堆的位置中工作时，请佩戴适当的防护装置。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/39939e805314706c953477ff63c8f1f0.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/39939e805314706c953477ff63c8f1f0.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/39939e805314706c953477ff63c8f1f0.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warfare吊门变体</h2>一系列大型网格机库门。 设计目的是适应任何布置并促进更复杂的模块化设计。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/34042640a1d7f63d6f36ef010f7ef448.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/34042640a1d7f63d6f36ef010f7ef448.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/34042640a1d7f63d6f36ef010f7ef448.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warfare火箭发射器</h2>视觉上独特而轻巧的火箭舱。 以时尚的方式带来破坏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/1fd85276bfa9fc63b98a9c7f0b683fb4.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/1fd85276bfa9fc63b98a9c7f0b683fb4.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/1fd85276bfa9fc63b98a9c7f0b683fb4.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warfare加特林机枪</h2>一种现代化的加特林机枪设计。 枪管加长，手感更重。 加特林机枪的旋转枪管从未如此好看。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/16b7e5e9fa6dc7b13e6b6b5892ffeaf2.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/16b7e5e9fa6dc7b13e6b6b5892ffeaf2.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/16b7e5e9fa6dc7b13e6b6b5892ffeaf2.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探照灯 </h2>一种铰接式聚光灯，其行为类似于炮塔。 能够在有限范围内跟踪目标。 装备齐全，拥有所有标准聚光灯功能，包括自定义颜色、闪烁设置、强度滑块等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/3540ac4ea199570ef810ec16d8476569.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/3540ac4ea199570ef810ec16d8476569.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/3540ac4ea199570ef810ec16d8476569.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >桥窗</h2>一种在视觉上更坚固的窗户版本。 提供桥窗斜面和桥窗正面。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/bae5e06fb327dcf07327338c9cb335b8.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/bae5e06fb327dcf07327338c9cb335b8.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/bae5e06fb327dcf07327338c9cb335b8.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >乘客长椅</h2>运兵车式的乘客座椅。 可以将多个座位布置为长椅。 设计的目的是无缝拼接在一起并为多名工程师提供座位。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/e88f2f38e25a17e98bf6891b8dafcad6.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/e88f2f38e25a17e98bf6891b8dafcad6.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/e88f2f38e25a17e98bf6891b8dafcad6.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >灯光面板</h2>现有照明解决方案的替代方案。 适用于带通道方块的天花板装饰。 采用小巧的外形设计，非常适合紧凑的空间。 也可以兼作迪斯科舞池！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/d683cff9b675a2e0e27135c26f53949c.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/d683cff9b675a2e0e27135c26f53949c.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/d683cff9b675a2e0e27135c26f53949c.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >舵</h2>一个崭新驾驶舱。 一个真正的指挥站。 以时尚的方式下达或接受命令。 “掌舵 108！”<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/609b40e0deb89159a5981047de211347.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/609b40e0deb89159a5981047de211347.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/609b40e0deb89159a5981047de211347.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warfare电池</h2>用这款全新而时尚的电池给你的轨道炮充电。 满足你的所有电能需求。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/6092612d9c22149d82f54c0a07883409.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/6092612d9c22149d82f54c0a07883409.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/6092612d9c22149d82f54c0a07883409.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >散热口</h2>在通风口打开时提供“一目了然”的电源使用情况，并根据电能需求喷射出系统热量。 非常适合光线不足的反应堆室。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/ddb8a494ce06e08896c6e12bcfbb5855.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/ddb8a494ce06e08896c6e12bcfbb5855.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/ddb8a494ce06e08896c6e12bcfbb5855.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >滑动舱门</h2>单一的大舱壁门。 这种重工业风格的门只有一个小舷窗供观察。 非常适合留住空气，或其他东西… <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/70e5a43f6df5597859566aa3c374baa6.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/70e5a43f6df5597859566aa3c374baa6.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/70e5a43f6df5597859566aa3c374baa6.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >林地迷彩装甲皮肤</h2>一种林地迷彩皮肤。 掩护你的坦克、火炮炮位或隐藏的前哨。 可以更改颜色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/0b72da65f11f281ae99864d0c553139b.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/0b72da65f11f281ae99864d0c553139b.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/0b72da65f11f281ae99864d0c553139b.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鲨鱼嘴头盔皮肤</h2>这就像猎人追逐他的猎物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/416a83e7eb7375fc9abb3bba24f07ce0.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/416a83e7eb7375fc9abb3bba24f07ce0.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/416a83e7eb7375fc9abb3bba24f07ce0.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“剪刀石头布”表情</h2>一种“pvp”表情，用于决定谁需要继续下一次采矿或者在战斗中担任指挥。 随机选择并显示石头、布或剪刀动画之一。 还可以使用 /rock、/paper、/scissors 聊天命令显示特定动画。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/45f3644fe616077945f7c85fdc7a2140.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/45f3644fe616077945f7c85fdc7a2140.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/45f3644fe616077945f7c85fdc7a2140.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“敬礼”表情</h2>站起来向你的盟友、敌人或光荣的死者敬礼<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/ce95fea06e5840c71b2ea39c504f8e3b.poster.avif?t=1739191609\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/ce95fea06e5840c71b2ea39c504f8e3b.webm?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783760/extras/ce95fea06e5840c71b2ea39c504f8e3b.mp4?t=1739191609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
